properties.name: Boise Art Museum
properties.description: Boise Art Museum BAM's Permanent Collection of 2,300 works of art focuses on 20th century American art with a long-standing emphasis on artists of the Pacific Northwest, American Realism and ceramics. BAM's Collection also includes a survey of European and non-Western artwork designed to provide a broader context for the overall Collection. Web site: http://boiseartmuseum.org/ For illustration only. User to verify all information.
